oday. The name link will take you directly to that entry on the directory home page.</li><li>Upcoming Birthdays &#8211;Birthdayswith the date. Does not show the birthdayshappening today. The name link will take you directly to that entry on the directory home page.</li><li>Recently Added &#8212; The ten newest entries.The name link will take you directly to that entry on the directory home page.</li><li>RecentlyModified&#8211; The ten most recently updated.The name link will take you directly to that entry on the directory home page.</li></ol><p><a href=\"/wp-content/uploads/Screen-Cature-Available-Widgets.png\"><img width=\"220\" height=\"150\" alt=\"\" src=\"/wp-content/themes/striking/includes/timthumb.php?src=/wp-content/uploads/Screen-Cature-Available-Widgets.png&amp;h=150&amp;w=220&amp;zc=1\" /></a><a href=\"/wp-content/uploads/Sceen-Capture-Simple-Search.png\"><img width=\"220\" height=\"150\" alt=\"\" src=\"/wp-content/themes/striking/includes/timthumb.php?src=/wp-content/uploads/Sceen-Capture-Simple-Search.png&amp;h=150&amp;w=220&amp;zc=1\" /></a><a href=\"/wp-content/uploads/Sceen-Capture-Todays-Anniversaries.png\"><img width=\"220\" height=\"150\" alt=\"\" src=\"/wp-content/themes/striking/includes/timthumb.php?src=/wp-content/uploads/Sceen-Capture-Todays-Anniversaries.png&amp;h=150&amp;w=220&amp;zc=1\" /></a><a href=\"/wp-content/uploads/Sceen-Capture-Upcoming-Anniversaeries.png\"><img width=\"220\" height=\"150\" alt=\"\" src=\"/wp-content/themes/striking/includes/timthumb.php?src=/wp-content/uploads/Sceen-Capture-Upcoming-Anniversaeries.png&amp;h=150&amp;w=220&amp;zc=1\" /></a><a href=\"/wp-content/uploads/Sceen-Capture-Todays-Birthdays.png\"><img width=\"220\" height=\"150\" alt=\"\" src=\"/wp-content/themes/striking/includes/timthumb.php?src=/wp-content/uploads/Sceen-Capture-Todays-Birthdays.png&amp;h=150&amp;w=220&amp;zc=1\" /></a><a href=\"/wp-content/uploads/Sceen-Capture-Upcoming-Birthdays.png\"><img width=\"220\" height=\"150\" alt=\"\" src=\"/w