(67,	1,	'2014-03-19 15:35:00',	'2014-03-19 15:35:00',	'<span style=\"color: #800000;\"><strong style=\"font-size: 14pt;\">Register Your Business</strong></span>\r\n\r\nThe <strong>Cougar Business Network</strong> is an online searchable database of Cougar-owned or -managed businesses located around the world that helps to facilitate Cougars doing business with Cougars. Visitors can search the Cougar Business Networkby business category and/or by location. You must be a current WSUAA Member to be listed.\r\n\r\n<hr/>\r\n<div>Please register as either a CBN member or a CBN affiliate. To register as a CBN member, the business must be Cougar-owned, -managed, or WSU alumni must be the principal executive(s) in a leadership role. To register as a CBN affiliate you must have a service or product you wish to offer WSU alumni, but are not the business or company owner. You must be a current member of the WSUAA when registering as an affiliate.</div>\r\n<br/>\r\n\r\n[connections_form logo=\'true\' default_type=\'organization\' select_type=\'false\' anniversary=\'true\' birthday=\'false\' notes=\'true\' str_contact_name=\'Business Contact Information\' str_bio=\'Business Description\']',	'Register',	'',	'inherit',	'open',	'open',	'',	'9-revision-v1',	'',	'',	'2014-03-19 15:35:00',	'2014-03-19 15:35:00',	'',	9,	'http://dev.cbn.wsu.edu/2014/03/9-revision-v1/',	0,	'revision',	'',	0);
